      <levelledPara>
        <title>General</title>
        <para>
          ATA Chapter 02 - Operations Information provides general operational guidance and procedures for the AMPEL360 BWB H₂ Hy-E Q100 aircraft. This chapter includes aircraft limitations, performance data, and operating procedures.
        </para>
      </levelledPara>
      <levelledPara>
        <title>Aircraft Overview</title>
        <para>
          The AMPEL360 BWB H₂ Hy-E Q100 is a revolutionary blended wing body aircraft powered by hydrogen fuel cells. Key features include:
        </para>
        <para>
          <randomList>
            <listItem><para>Blended Wing Body design for 30% improved aerodynamic efficiency</para></listItem>
            <listItem><para>Hydrogen (H₂) fuel cell propulsion system - zero emissions</para></listItem>
            <listItem><para>CO₂ capture system for carbon-negative flight</para></listItem>
            <listItem><para>CAOS (Computer Aided Operations &amp; Services) AI system integration</para></listItem>
            <listItem><para>Passenger capacity: 220 passengers</para></listItem>
            <listItem><para>Range: 4,000 km (2,160 NM)</para></listItem>
          </randomList>
        </para>
      </levelledPara>
      <levelledPara>
        <title>Operations Philosophy</title>
        <para>
          All operations are conducted with emphasis on:
        </para>
        <para>
          <randomList>
            <listItem><para>Safety - H₂ system safety is paramount</para></listItem>
            <listItem><para>Efficiency - Optimal fuel cell and energy management</para></listItem>
            <listItem><para>Environmental Responsibility - Carbon-negative operations</para></listItem>
            <listItem><para>AI-Assisted Decision Making - CAOS advisory system support</para></listItem>
          </randomList>
        </para>
      </levelledPara>
      <levelledPara>
        <title>Documentation Structure</title>
        <para>
          Operations and maintenance documentation follows S1000D standards and includes:
        </para>
        <para>
          <randomList>
            <listItem><para>Aircraft Maintenance Manual (AMM)</para></listItem>
            <listItem><para>Airplane Flight Manual (AFM)</para></listItem>
            <listItem><para>Flight Crew Operating Manual (FCOM)</para></listItem>
            <listItem><para>Quick Reference Handbook (QRH)</para></listItem>
            <listItem><para>CAOS Operations Manual</para></listItem>
          </randomList>
        </para>
      </levelledPara>
    </description>
